# whitespace-only-lines-consecutive

## Input

```
a 1
 
  
   
b 2

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..17
  ENTRY@0..4
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    INTEGER@2..3
      NUMERAL@2..3 "1"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
  SPACE@4..5 " "
  NEWLINE@5..6 "\n"
  SPACE@6..8 "  "
  NEWLINE@8..9 "\n"
  SPACE@9..12 "   "
  NEWLINE@12..13 "\n"
  ENTRY@13..17
    WORD_KEY@13..14
      WORD@13..14 "b"
    SPACE@14..15 " "
    INTEGER@15..16
      NUMERAL@15..16 "2"
    NEWLINE@16..17 "\n"
```

